skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: worse counter
des:
Let Alexa count for you!

Just say "Worse Counter, count to seven" and you will hear Alexa counting from one to seven.
You can also specify the start number by saying "Worse Counter, count from four to nine".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
